O mankind! Lo! the promise of Allâh is true. So let not the life of
the world beguile you, and let not the beguiler beguile you with
regard to Allâh.

Lo! Satan is an enemy to you, so treat him as an enemy. He only
summoneth his faction to be companions of the Flaming Fire.
